description: Adtelligent is a supply-side advertising technology company providing demand management and intermediation solutions for publishers. It provides ad integrating services for display and video and selling inventory services to programmatic buyers. It offers solutions including ad serving, ad monetization platform, and header bidding management platform for publishers.
